{"tid":1716911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【一路好走】黃泆潼：昨晚TG帶走了婆婆","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:20:46.000Z","uid":66271,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fe592ea4391ada220201a29217e646c0217c6191","tid":1716911,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191113/large/1573646593_e42b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573646593_e42b.jpg&h=b8c53eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾參選港姐、現年41歲的黃泆潼，在社交網發出控訴：「昨晚TG帶走了婆婆。Tear gas took my grandma's life last night.」<br />\n<br />\n黃泆潼分別用中、英文留言指控TG帶走了婆婆，有網民轉發並留言：「藝人黃泆潼嘅婆婆！黑警係唔會知道催淚彈嘅殺傷力有幾嚴重，一路好走！」《蘋果》致電向黃泆潼了解詳情，她在電話說：「Sorry，我唔答呀！多謝關心，唔回應。」問到心情是否好差？ 她即cut線。 而在她的社交網公開帖文，記者卻見不到這篇關於她婆婆的死訊，不知是只限朋友睇到，還是已經刪除呢！<br />\n<br />\n16歲被星探發掘做模特兒的黃泆潼，曾為譚詠麟MV擔任女主角，21歲參選港姐打入決賽後簽無綫，曾拍攝《戀愛星球人》、《仁心解碼》等劇集，08年離開大台後轉做唱片騎師，16年與著名獨立電子音樂人Kavemura結婚。 近月香港發生逆權運動，關心社會的黃泆潼，在社交網亦有貼全黑及黑底白字寫着「香港」的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n多區抗爭遍地開花，克警無止境以武力鎮壓示威者，連月來在多區狂放催淚彈肆虐，好多無辜市民只是上街，都可能會遇到催淚彈放題，在零裝備下不幸中招，加上有指警方疑用過期催淚彈，威脅市民健康。"},{"pid":"71cfaa87c47e55549c3ab23250e8b7778c8b6eae","tid":1716911,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e068c0cb25527368bee31ac04df44fb954ec4f2","tid":1716911,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"30f70a0dc41fff7dd46734dc3ccfb787f6546c64","tid":1716911,"uid":304443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"rip ..."},{"pid":"044f52a20bf945f2187f7699574677410f3c82e6","tid":1716911,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ba10bc02abc7041aad4f8eabef55647bc8dcab","tid":1716911,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"ea46f0bb3f6501b952557f713e3f60b34aefccf9","tid":1716911,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"bd10c8d8b54b11154d4f0b9392be0cedfbb4810e","tid":1716911,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"又要講又要刪!?"},{"pid":"b5e089a2755742295a2b6ef8803eb4fed32d7d4a","tid":1716911,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeab03f3cd617271d14269cbad7f25777988fa2","tid":1716911,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"1c6f4d01901bc446175e207eb9bd77e071e1cda1","tid":1716911,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"Rip..."},{"pid":"085d22b9a48534d66c7fcdffc66f09c33bd9590e","tid":1716911,"uid":76776,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5464036076272bad85843d1ef1dd0f9008ea997","tid":1716911,"uid":217270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2937b6e890796b62845a9c1ab5e75beaece14182","tid":1716911,"uid":158008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"085d22b9a48534d66c7fcdffc66f09c33bd9590e","tid":1716911,"uid":76776,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"你條5毛狗都幾撚得閒"},{"pid":"1d483dca17a0f6681107d03588f47dbd9a8a6293","tid":1716911,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":